{$B- Incomplete boolean evaluation}
{$P- No open string parameters}
{$Q- No arithmetic overflow checking}
{$T- No type-checked pointers}
{$V- No var string checking}
{$X+ Extended syntax}
{$Z- Enumeration size is 256}

